snippet.title: Candy Disaster 30s trailer (No Sub Ver.) - New Tower Defense Game
snippet.description: Candy Disaster is a 3D tower defense game that combines traps with a strategy to stop the candy zombies. Adventure to different plants, mix and match any traps with your strategy to create brand new combinations! Dozens of clever combinations to discover!
